The paper deals with biometric security and encryption, which are both topics related to computer security (cs.CR). The use of facial and iris biometrics also involves computer vision (cs.CV) and multimodal biometrics (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the trade-off between recognition accuracy and efficiency, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and information theory (cs.IT).
